	"This TAS is an improvement on the currently published 
	(__wikiLink|href=/7274S|implicitdisplaytext=7274S)
	", and uses the same general route to complete the game as fast as possible, while implementing two new strategies involving Chauncey, as well as saving a couple frames towards the end of the run. This submission overall is a ~35 second improvement, and brings the total TAS time down to under 9 minutes!
	$LF
